Package: pmbbEchoExtract
Title: Extract and Process PMBB Echocardiogram Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sarah Abramowitz", "abramows@pennmedicine.upenn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions for extracting, cleaning, filtering, and processing echocardiogram 
    data from the Penn Medicine BioBank (PMBB). Includes tools for data 
    formatting, outlier detection, and measurement standardization.
